[30;1m44 | [0m[35m    time. However, if we make it to the end of the request (without raising a[0m

[30;1m364 | [0m[35m    Applies patches to modules that were already imported prior to agent startup[0m
[30;1m365 | [0m[35m[0m
[30;1m366 | [0m[35m    Here's the problem: our patches don't get applied until after our[0m
